title: HOW DO WHITESTRIPS WORK BETTER THAN WHITENING TOOTHPASTE?
description: Using whitening toothpaste for 2 minutes doesn’t give whitening ingredients time to reach deep stains. But Crest Whitestrips can. That’s why they whiten 25x better.
